Curlew Multimedia Converter:
----------------------------

Description:
------------

Easy to use, Free and Open-Source Multimedia converter for Linux.


Dependencies:
-------------

- python >= 2.7 << 3.0
- python-gobject >= 3.0
- gir1.2-gtk-3.0
- ffmpeg >= 0.8 (or libav-tools >= 0.8)
- mencoder
- libavcodec-extra-53
- xdg-utils


License:
--------

Waqf public license.
Please see LICENSE-ar.txt/LICENSE-en files for more informations.


Installation:
-------------

Run script "install" as root. (ex: sudo ./install).


Remove:
-------

Run script "uninstall" as root. (ex: sudo ./uninstall).

